description: Phillip Aubrey is ready to listen, ready to obey. He knows tricks and doesn't mind the leash and collar one bit. Spencer Reed is a good pet owner who feeds his puppy all the meat he can handle, rubs his belly regularly, and makes sure his coat his spit shine clean and healthy. Then he fucks him across a table and cums in his mouth.Enjoy!
title: I Wanna Be Your Dog
